data.name: Message.KeepOpenWarning
data.value: Keep this window open until validation is complete!

data.name: Tooltip.ValidationExplanation
data.value: H5Ps must first be checked for functionality before they can be used successfully in a learning environment. This check determines whether points can be earned by answering questions (making the H5P completable) or whether it is non-completable where progress comes from simply navigating through slides. It is also possible that an H5P is faulty or does not display at all.
